com.unvired.ump.agent

Interface IUserSetting

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UserSetting, UserSetting

    public interface IUserSetting
extends java.io.Serializable
    IUserSetting provides a mechanism that allows process agents to read, delete or set a users application specific properties.
